# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Drakuul's Legacy
Event Quest6
Text "%C
Text "|10Drakuul's Legacy
Text
Text "|02Using the directions given to you by the acolyte, you find a hidden passage
Text "in the mines that leads to an old crypt.  The air is cold, the smell of
Text "death is overwhelming, and torches flicker weakly along the stone walls.
pause
Text
Text "You descend a narrow staircase and find yourself in a dark corridor lined
Text "with stone coffins.  Some of the lids have been pushed aside from within
Text "and you hear a low growl from the darkness ahead . . .
pause
Text
Text "Several ghouls emerge from the shadows!
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 0
AddEnemy /m/Eva 0
AddEnemy /m/Eva 1
AddEnemy /m/Eva 1
AddEnemy /m/Eva 36
AddEnemy /m/Eva 36
Fight NextLine STOP STOP
Text
Text "|02You push deeper into the crypt and the corridor opens into a large burial
Text "chamber where several pale figures stand motionless among the coffins.
Text "Their eyes glow red as they notice your presence.
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 54
AddEnemy /m/Eva 54
AddEnemy /m/Eva 54
{R40}AddEnemy /m/Eva 54
Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
Text
Text "|02After destroying the vampire spawns, you press forward through a heavy
Text "iron door and find a chapel that has been desecrated.  Black candles burn
Text "with an unnatural flame and two guards stand watch before a stone altar.
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 55
AddEnemy /m/Eva 55
Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
Text
Text "|02The guards are destroyed, but before you can catch your breath a deep
Text "voice echoes through the chamber.
Text
Text "|10"You dare enter my domain?  No mortal has left this place alive!"
pause
Text
Text "|02You notice the desecrated altar still glows with dark energy.  Perhaps you
Text "could use it against the vampire somehow . . .
Text
Text " (|05D|02)estroy the altar before facing Darkuul
Text " (|05F|02)ace Darkuul directly
Text
Prompt "[|12DF|02]: |13
Option D Quest6.Altar
Option F Quest6.Face
End

        Result Quest6.Altar
        Text
        Text "|02You overturn the altar and smash it to pieces.  The dark energy
        Text "crackles wildly and dissipates.  A terrible shriek echoes from deeper
        Text "in the crypt.  Without the altar's power sustaining him, Darkuul is
        Text "weakened!
        Text
        Text "|02The vampire staggers into the chapel, his form flickering.
        Text
        Text "|10"What have you done?!" |02he hisses.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 56
        Fight Quest6.Win Quest6.Lose NoRun
        End

        Result Quest6.Face
        Text
        Text "|02A tall figure steps out from behind the altar.  His skin is pale as
        Text "death and his eyes burn with a crimson fire.  A vampire spawn hisses
        Text "from the shadows beside him.  Darkuul bares his fangs and both
        Text "creatures lunge towards you!
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 54
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 56
        Fight Quest6.FaceWin Quest6.Lose NoRun
        End

        Result Quest6.FaceWin
        Text
        Text "|02You search the intact altar and find |10500 gold pieces |02hidden
        Text "within a compartment in its base!
        GiveGold 500
        Jump Quest6.Win
        End

        Result Quest6.Win
        Text
        Text "|02Darkuul lets out a terrible shriek as he crumbles to dust before your
        Text "eyes.  The black candles extinguish themselves and the crypt falls silent.
        pause
        Text
        Text "You return to town to deliver the good news.  The townspeople celebrate
        Text "and the acolyte thanks you personally.  |03(You gain 2500 gold and 75
        Text "points!  You also gain 1 monster fight!)
        GiveGold 2500
        GivePoints 75
        GiveFight 1
        AddNews "|10 The vampire Darkuul has been destroyed!
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest6.Lose
        Text "|02The last thing you see is Darkuul's terrible grin as the world
        Text "goes dark . . .
        End

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Quest for the Lost King
Event Quest7
Text "%C
Text "|10The Quest for the Lost King
Text
Text "|02Following the knight's directions, you descend into the deepest corridors
Text "of the mines.  The walls change from rough stone to polished black marble
Text "and you know you are nearing The Dark One's domain.
pause
Text
Text "You come upon a large iron gate flanked by two guards in black armor who
Text "draw their swords the moment they see you.
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 67
AddEnemy /m/Eva 67
AddEnemy /m/Eva 67
{R30}AddEnemy /m/Eva 67
Fight NextLine STOP STOP
Text
Text "|02Beyond the gate lies a dungeon.  You can hear moaning from cells deeper
Text "within.  A side passage leads to what looks like a jailer's quarters.
Text
Text " (|05S|02)earch the jailer's quarters for keys
Text " (|05P|02)ress on towards the cells immediately
Text
Prompt "[|12SP|02]: |13
Option S Quest7.Search
Option P Quest7.Press
End

        Result Quest7.Search
        Text
        Text "|02You enter the jailer's quarters and find a brutish man gnawing on
        Text "a bone who sees you and rises with a snarl.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 68
        Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
        Text
        Text "|02You search his body and find a ring of keys.  |03(You also find 200
        Text "gold pieces hidden under his mattress!)
        GiveGold 200
        Jump Quest7.Knight
        End

        Result Quest7.Press
        Text
        Text "|02You press deeper into the dungeon, stepping past empty cells.  You
        Text "will need to find keys further in.
        Jump Quest7.Knight
        End

        Result Quest7.Knight
        Text
        Text "|02As you move towards the deepest cells, a dark knight in armor that
        Text "gleams with an unnatural sheen blocks your path.
        Text
        Text "|10"None shall free the king while I draw breath!" |02he bellows.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 69
        Fight NextLine Quest7.Lose NoRun
        Text
        Text "|02You defeat the dark knight and his armor shatters into pieces.  Using the
        Text "keys, you begin checking the cells until you find an old man in tattered
        Text "robes in the deepest cell.  Despite his condition, he carries himself with
        Text "dignity.
        pause
        Text
        Text "|10"I am King Claudius.  I have waited many years for this day." |02he says
        Text "with a weary smile.
        pause
        Chat _King
        Text
        Text "|02You escort the king out of the dungeon and back to safety, and the
        Text "townspeople are overjoyed at the news of his rescue.
        Text "|03(You gain 2000 gold pieces and 75 points!)
        GiveGold 2000
        GivePoints 75
        SetFlag P2
        AddNews "|10 King Claudius has been rescued from the dungeon!
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest7.Lose
        Text "|02The dark knight is too powerful.  You are dragged into one of the
        Text "dungeon cells . . .
        End

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Quest for the Lost Knight
Event Quest8
Text "%C
Text "|10The Quest for the Lost Knight
Text
Text "|02Following the village idiot's directions, you travel north of town to an
Text "abandoned stone keep.  The building is crumbling and overgrown with vines,
Text "and the front door hangs from one hinge.
pause
Text
Text "You enter the keep and find it mostly empty, with broken furniture and old
Text "weapons littering the floor.  You hear a faint voice calling for help from
Text "somewhere below.
Text
