# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Spirits of Lovers
Event Quest10
Text "%C
Text "|10The Spirits of Lovers
Text
Text "|02You find the cave from the seamstress's story on the snowy hillside.  The
Text "entrance is partially blocked by old snow, but you manage to squeeze through.
Text "Inside, the air is freezing cold and you can see your breath.
pause
Text
Text "You walk deeper into the cave.  The sound of dripping water echoes around
Text "you.  Then you hear something else -- a faint sobbing.
pause
Text
Text "A ghostly figure appears before you.  It is a woman in a tattered dress,
Text "weeping silently.  She looks up and sees you.
Text
Text "|10"Please . . . I fell into this chasm long ago and my beloved took his
Text "own life in grief.  I cannot rest until we are together again."
Text
Text "|02 (|05H|02)elp the spirit find peace
Text " (|05T|02)ake the treasure you can see behind her
Text
Prompt "[|12HT|02]: |13
Option H Quest10.Help
Option T Quest10.Take
End

        Result Quest10.Help
        Text
        Text "|02You agree to help.  The ghost leads you deeper into the cave to a
        Text "wide chasm.  A dark presence lurks at the bottom, preventing the lovers
        Text "from reuniting.  You must destroy it.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        Fight NextLine STOP STOP
        Text
        Text "|02You descend carefully into the chasm.  At the bottom, a swirling mass
        Text "of darkness hovers over the woman's remains.  The dark presence turns
        Text "towards you with malice.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 44
        Fight NextLine Quest10.Lose NoRun
        Text
        Text "|02The dark presence shatters and the cave fills with a warm light.  The
        Text "spirit of the woman's beloved appears beside her and they embrace at
        Text "last.  Together, they rise upward and fade into the light.
        pause
        Text
        Text "A feeling of peace washes over the clan.  |03(Each clansman's skill points
        Text "are restored!)
        Heal SP
        Text
        Text "|02Among the remains you find |101000 gold pieces|02.  |03(You gain 75 points
        Text "for helping the spirits find peace!)
        GiveGold 1000
        GivePoints 75
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest10.Take
        Text
        Text "|02You push past the ghost and grab at the treasure.  The spirit lets out
        Text "a terrible wail!  The cave grows dark and cold as several ghosts
        Text "materialize around you.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 43
        Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
        Text
        Text "|02The ghosts fade away reluctantly.  You grab what treasure you can find
        Text "and make for the exit.  The sobbing resumes behind you as you leave.
        Text "You can't help feeling a twinge of guilt.
        Text "|03(You gain 1000 gold pieces and 50 points.)
        GiveGold 1000
        GivePoints 50
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest10.Lose
        Text "|02The darkness overwhelms you.  You wake up outside the cave, shivering
        Text "and confused . . .
        End

