pause
Text
Text "|02You grasp the Heavenly Sword.  It feels warm in your hands, as if it has
Text "been waiting for you.  The blade pulses with light as you lift it from the
Text "pedestal.
Text
Text "|03(You gain the Heavenly Sword!  You also gain 3500 gold pieces
Text "and 75 points!)
GiveItem Heavenly Sword
GiveGold 3500
GivePoints 75
SetFlag P3
AddNews "|10 The Heavenly Sword has been recovered from the mines!
DoneQuest
End

        Result Quest18.Lose
        Text "|02The sword guardian is far too powerful.  You are not yet worthy of
        Text "the Heavenly Sword . . .
        End

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Poet's Quill
Event Quest19
Text "%C
Text "|10The Poet's Quill
Text
Text "|02Using the poet's description, you search the mines for the thieves who stole
Text "his golden quill.  After some time, you spot a trail of dropped coins
Text "leading down a side corridor and you follow it.
pause
Text
Text "The trail leads to a makeshift camp where several thief scouts sit around
Text "a fire.  They jump up as they notice you!
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 39
AddEnemy /m/Eva 39
AddEnemy /m/Eva 39
{R40}AddEnemy /m/Eva 39
Fight NextLine STOP STOP
Text
Text "|02You search the camp but find no quill, although one of the fallen thieves
Text "mutters something about a hideout deeper in the mines.  You press forward.
pause
Text
Text "You reach a dead end with a large wooden door and kick it in to find the
Text "thief leader sitting at a desk, examining the golden quill.  He sees you
Text "and draws his sword.
Text
Text "|10"That quill is worth a fortune!  You'll have to pry it from my cold dead
Text "hands!" |02he snarls.
Text
Text " (|05F|02)ight him for the quill
Text " (|05N|02)egotiate -- offer gold for its return
Text
Prompt "[|12FN|02]: |13
Option F Quest19.Fight
Option N Quest19.Negotiate
End

        Result Quest19.Fight
        Text
        Text "|02You draw your weapons and charge.
        pause
        AddEnemy /m/Eva 40
        Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
        Text
        Text "|02The thief leader falls and you pick up the golden quill from the desk.
        Text "It is beautiful, made from the feather of a rare golden bird, and you
        Text "also find |10600 gold pieces |02stashed under the desk.
        Text
        Text "|02You return the quill to the grateful poet.  |03(You gain 600 gold pieces
        Text "and 50 points!)
        GiveGold 600
        GivePoints 50
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest19.Negotiate
        Text
        Text "|02The thief leader eyes you suspiciously.
        Text
        {!$300}Text "|10"You don't even have enough gold to make it worth my while!" |02he
        {!$300}Text "laughs.  |02Looks like you'll have to fight after all.
        {!$300}pause
        {!$300}Jump Quest19.Fight
        {$300}Text "|10"300 gold and you can have the quill.  Deal?" |02he says.
        {$300}Text
        {$300}Prompt "|02Pay the 300 gold? [|12Y/N|02]: |13
        {$300}Option Y Quest19.Pay
        {$300}Option N Quest19.Fight
        End

        Result Quest19.Pay
        Text
        Text "|02You hand over 300 gold pieces.  The thief leader smirks and tosses you
        Text "the quill.  |10"Pleasure doing business with ya!" |02he says.
        TakeGold 300
        Text
        Text "|02You return the quill to the poet.  He is overjoyed that you resolved it
        Text "without bloodshed and gives you a generous reward.
        Text "|03(You gain 200 gold pieces and 75 points!)
        GiveGold 200
        GivePoints 75
        DoneQuest
        End

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The Dark One
Event Quest20
Text "%C
Text "|10The Dark One
Text
Text "|02The time has come.  You descend into the deepest reaches of the mines,
Text "beyond the ruins of the Orc Lord's fortress and the sealed realm of the
Text "Demon Lord, to the domain of The Dark One himself -- the one who destroyed
Text "the Old Kingdom and the fifth and greatest of the Five Great Evils.
pause
Text
Text "The walls here are made of black obsidian that reflects no light, and the
Text "only illumination comes from veins of red energy that pulse through the
Text "stone like blood through veins.
pause
Text
Text "You enter a wide corridor and are immediately set upon by dark minions!
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
{R40}AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
{R20}AddEnemy /m/Eva 74
Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
Text
Text "|02You push through the minions and enter a great hall lit by black flames
Text "where dark sorcerers chant in a circle, channeling energy towards a
Text "massive door at the far end.
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 75
AddEnemy /m/Eva 75
{R40}AddEnemy /m/Eva 75
Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
Text
Text "|02The sorcerers are silenced and their dark energy dissipates.  You approach
Text "the massive door and push it open.
pause
Text
Text "Beyond the door lies an arena of black stone where the dark champion, the
Text "personal guard of The Dark One, stands in the center and draws a massive
Text "black sword.
Text
Text "|10"My master awaits beyond.  But you shall not pass." |02he says coldly.
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 76
Fight NextLine STOP NoRun
Text
Text "|02The champion falls and you step over his body into the final chamber.
pause
Text
Text "|02The chamber is vast and empty except for a throne of black crystal at the
Text "far end.  On the throne sits a figure cloaked in shadow who rises slowly,
Text "and two red eyes peer out from beneath his hood.
Text
Text "|10"So . . . you are the one who destroyed my servants.  The Orc Lord.  The
Text "Wyvern Lord.  The Dragon Lord.  The Demon Lord.  You even freed that fool
Text "Claudius." |02he speaks, his voice like ice.
pause
{P3}Text
{P3}Text "|02The Dark One's eyes narrow as he sees the Heavenly Sword in your hands.
{P3}Text
{P3}Text "|10"The Heavenly Sword!  Impossible!  No matter . . . I destroyed its master
{P3}Text "once before.  I shall do so again!"
{!P3}Text
{!P3}Text "|10"You come to face me without even the Heavenly Sword?  Your courage is
{!P3}Text "admirable, if foolish."
pause
Text
Text "|02The Dark One throws off his cloak.  Beneath it is a being of pure shadow
Text "and malice.  Dark energy crackles around his form as he draws a blade of
Text "black flame.  The final battle begins!
pause
AddEnemy /m/Eva 77
Fight Quest20.Win Quest20.Lose NoRun
End

        Result Quest20.Win
        Text
        Text "|02The Dark One staggers backwards, his form flickering like a dying flame.
        Text
        {P3}Text "|10"The sword . . . how can this be . . . I am eternal . . ."
        {!P3}Text "|10"Impossible . . . no mortal could . . ."
        Text
        Text "|02His body dissolves into shadow and the shadow itself burns away in a
        Text "flash of white light.  The chamber shakes violently as cracks appear in
        Text "the black crystal throne and it shatters into a thousand pieces.
        pause
        Text
        Text "|02The red veins of energy in the walls fade and die, and the black
        Text "obsidian crumbles to ordinary stone.  The domain of The Dark One is no
        Text "more.
        pause
        Text
        Text "|02You make your way back to the surface and as you emerge from the mines
        Text "the townspeople gather around you.  Word spreads quickly -- The Dark One
        Text "is destroyed and the realm is saved.
        pause
        Text
        Text "|03(You gain 5000 gold pieces, 75 points, and 1 monster fight!)
        GiveGold 5000
        GivePoints 75
        GiveFight 1
        SetFlag G0
        AddNews "|10 The Dark One has been destroyed!  The realm is saved!
        DoneQuest
        End

        Result Quest20.Lose
        Text "|02The Dark One's power is unlike anything you have ever faced.  You
        Text "are overwhelmed and cast out of his domain.
        Text
        Text "|10"Run, little mortals.  Tell them what awaits those who challenge me."
        End

